    public enum FilterOption
extends java.lang.Enum<FilterOption>
    This class is for a enum object : FilterOption. There are five options to filter the data on the server: 1.get Max For Scenario. 2.get My Last Game. 3.get My Best. 4.get All My Best. 5. getAllBest.
